## Limitations

This report is based on information available up to October 2023 and may not account for more recent developments in the global economy. Additionally, the complexity of inflation means that not all contributing factors may be fully captured in this analysis. The report relies on publicly available sources, which may have inherent biases or limitations in their reporting.